    <description>Package Description</description>
    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10788: [HptpCapturePackets] Adding three params so users can prevent the test class from reading amble pa...'
'Merged PR 10747: [CaptureVector] Adding workaround for extra bits in CTV'
'Merged PR 9787: Query IsPatternAnAmble from pattern fail data (Prime 13)'
'Merged PR 10124: [57113] [Prime.TestMethods.Capture] Removed 'exit port 2' on test pass - to 13.xx.xx'
'Merged PR 10130: Commit 8d234751: Merged PR 10111: Fixing CaptureVectorTest to exit Port 2 when CTV is all zero  Before this, when CTV bits returned all zero, the test method still exit through port 1. This is not align with how Evergreen worked.  This PR is meant to fix that. Making the test method to exit to port 2 when all CTV bits are zero.'
'Merged PR 9430: Fix exception when no CTV data is returned by TOS'
'Merged PR 9341: Merged PR 9334: [CaptureVector] Fixing double scope for idut pins in capture...'</releaseNotes>
